Deathrun_Crash_Medieval
=======================

Original map created by [T]incho for CS1.6
With permission, fully recreated wth new features for CS:S by me!

A lovely deathrun map recreated from the PS1 game "Crash bandicoot" themed just like in the game, with avarage difficulty, 20+ traps and 3 mninigames at the end for survivors.
Also there are secret grenades, and ofcourse the crash bandicoot crystal with a nice feature.

Hope you like the map, i spend a lot of time on :)
Have fun!

For more info on [T]incho: https://www.facebook.com/deathrun1.6
